    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/de8d2173d37887ccb82b21ba01423d25.poster.avif?t=1758970451\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/de8d2173d37887ccb82b21ba01423d25.webm?t=1758970451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/de8d2173d37887ccb82b21ba01423d25.mp4?t=1758970451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >作战概要</h2><strong>以神风攻击，杀出胜利之路！</strong><br>没什么好害怕的。替代的多的是。<br>以多彩，个性丰富的武器清光敌人，最后将自身化身为肉弹，轰轰烈烈地牺牲自己！<br><br>人类史上首款。<br>一边盛大的把周围卷进爆炸中，一边朝终点爆冲的，自爆系STG。<br><br><strong>全员，突击－！</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2>世界大战爆发后已经过了100年。<br>战火丝毫完全没有平息的迹象。<br><br>战场的主角，从人类悄悄换成自律兵器，战争也更加趋于火热。<br>自我增殖的兵器，被自我增殖的兵器摧毁……<br>那样的毫无意义的重复与循环，彷彿将永无止尽。<br><br>就在那之中，一台人型兵器开口说话了。<br><strong>“诶，是谁吃掉我的布丁了？”</strong><br><br>这句话，成为长久战局的转折点了……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/12def07074d6151e8bc23e6b1e526e59.avif?t=1758970451\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br><strong>樱花</strong> <br>被冠以横须贺MXY-7 OHKA之名的可抛弃式量产型特别攻击机。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/cb3fb2a1cb4667b59823965a92e1fe1e.avif?t=1758970451\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br><strong>梅花</strong> <br>个性纤细又爱哭的特别攻撃机。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/e0e0bf60e19310a1b64bff605bd01063.avif?t=1758970451\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br><strong>彩</strong><br>喜爱布丁的沉着冷静的策略家。担任吐嘈。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/f20b1d3d50605126536ad939af3d890d.avif?t=1758970451\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br><strong>燕</strong><br>和彩一起行动的小小的战友<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/49cead5ed2a69715905f7e5f0a7f5c2f.avif?t=1758970451\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br><strong>零</strong><br>掌握左右战局的关键的神秘少女。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >系统</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/53348698318182e710c4a9784a5f0d33.poster.avif?t=1758970451\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/53348698318182e710c4a9784a5f0d33.webm?t=1758970451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/53348698318182e710c4a9784a5f0d33.mp4?t=1758970451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>以武器击倒敌人，开出自己的灿烂之路吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/ed6ac5c384907b1e0c103e23676bd489.poster.avif?t=1758970451\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/ed6ac5c384907b1e0c103e23676bd489.webm?t=1758970451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031720/extras/ed6ac5c384907b1e0c103e23676bd489.mp4?t=1758970451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>中弹是获得名誉的入手机会！ </strong><br>将自身化身为肉弹，勇猛的朝向可恨敌人冲进去吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特徵</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>驱使武器与神风攻击，各个关卡尽可能的快速过关，尽可能拖住众多敌人爆死的，前所未见STG。<br></li><li>自机数无限！盛大的将周围敌人一起卷入自爆攻击，体验痛快爽快游戏感。<br></li><li>时间、出击数、击破分数，三种评价系统。<br></li><li>含三种结局，共50个关卡。<br></li><li>由Q版角色们所带来，既可爱又杀气腾腾的剧情对话。<br></li><li>视场景需求灵活切换，多种类型的丰富武器。</li></ul>",
